M a n B i r d â„¢ 2024-07-12 2:18 AM
for something like drums where theres lots of elements contributing to it , usually you dont want to process them all very differently and have them all thru different reverbs for example. that creates a bit of a disconnect between the elements. so even if youre not going for a live sound and more electronic or something, its still good to pay attention to how they work and sit together
2:20 AM
